Description: pyglins
        =======
        
        Minimal plugin system for Python apps
        
        Using pyglins
        -------------
        
        .. code:: python
        
            import pyglins
        
            pyglins.scan_for_plugins('test/plugins')
            for plugin in pyglins.BasePlugin.plugins:
                loaded_plugin = plugin()
                loaded_plugin.run()
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        ::
        
            pip install git+https://github.com/paxet/pyglins.git
        
